Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.49,0:21:12.48,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}纵使深陷天大的谎言中
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.48,0:21:16.60,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想爱下去
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.87,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}夜色满溢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.13,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}配合着步伐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.13,0:21:27.95,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}时钟停摆 淡淡的诅咒缠绕着我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.95,0:21:32.46,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}你的反应总是在逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.98,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果只是想重来而已
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.98,0:21:41.30,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}那你这样吊着我又是何必
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.30,0:21:45.84,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我想知道我的心该放在哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.84,0:21:50.35,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}迟早都会迎来结束
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.35,0:21:53.17,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我早就清清楚楚
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.17,0:21:54.90,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}包括那些不和的信号
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.90,0:21:58.60,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我们和好吧 别再冷战了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.60,0:22:02.78,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我讨厌和你这样拉扯下去
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.78,0:22:06.79,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}纵使深陷天大的谎言中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.79,0:22:11.16,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想爱下去
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.37,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3)}夜色满溢
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.37,0:22:16.44,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}在这个不知余年多少的今天
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.44,0:22:22.67,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我只想要你能让我继续思念你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:40.54,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}话都堵在了喉咙里
